    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/04/125391187/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_671757157680424296.png",
                "id": "talent46132",
                "key": "冰錐迸射",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰錐迸射"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素傷害</span>，本角色附屬<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">四迸冰錐</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">四迸冰錐</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">角色進行普通攻擊時：</span>對所有敵方後臺角色造成1點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/04/125391187/0124980d7537e933e9e0e819b78a0733_6296268481348483260.png",
                "id": "talent54339",
                "key": "圓舞冰環",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "圓舞冰環"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素傷害</span>，對所有敵方後臺角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span>，召喚<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">刺擊冰稜</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/04/125391187/77df8fb6101bdb6c35d501967b98f941_6220107641756335545.png",
                "id": "talent4814",
                "key": "冰稜轟墜",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰稜轟墜"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">被動技能</span></p><p>【被動】戰鬥開始時，初始附屬<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">冰晶核心</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">冰晶核心</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">所附屬角色被擊倒時：</span>移除此效果，使角色<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">免於被擊倒</span>，並治療該角色到1點生命值。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/04/125391187/c9fb58d0c17579d0eca97a167035bc53_1874181600529433259.png",
                "id": "talent21367",
                "key": "冰晶核心",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰晶核心"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>對敵方<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">距離我方出戰角色最近的角色</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/04/125391187/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_9050583505816528418.png",
                "id": "talent69825",
                "key": "刺擊冰稜",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/04/125391187/9a3a650b50940ebaf9e842bccc80f213_8861970271547233419.png",
                "title": "刺擊冰稜"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超導</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">凍結</span>：本傷害+1，使目標本回合無法行動（受到<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>傷害后提前解除，但是傷害+2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/04/125391187/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_6693420054746245062.png",
                "id": "talent7050",
                "key": "冰元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透傷害</span></strong></p><p>穿透傷害無法受到傷害加成，但是也無法被護盾、傷害免疫等效果抵消。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">距離我方出戰角色最近的角色</span></strong></p><p>對方場上距離我方出戰角色「最近」的角色，指的是位置與我方出戰角色最接近的敵方角色。</p><p>如果存在多個位置最接近的角色，則其中靠前的角色被視為「最近」。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">免於被擊倒</span></strong></p><p>一些效果會使角色在生命值被降為0的時候<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">免於被擊倒</span>，並治療該角色到一定生命值。</p><p>此時，角色不視為被<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">擊倒</span>過。（因此，角色所附屬的裝備和狀態不會被棄置，充能也不會被清空。）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/04/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_7003630862797490305.png",
                "id": "talent90491",
